citances.sentence: 1 This proceeding was heard at the same time as The Wilderness Society Inc. v The Hon. Malcolm Turnbull, Minister for the Environment and Water Resources [2007] FCA 1178 (TWS proceeding). These reasons for judgment are to be read together with the reasons for judgment published in the TWS proceeding. Terms defined in the reasons for judgment in the TWS proceeding have the same meaning in these reasons for judgment.
